{"descriptions":[{"id":1199,"title":null,"content":"\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eThe present tense is formed by placing after the verb the particles: \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་ཡོད་རེད་\u003c/span\u003e (assertive), \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་འདུག་ \u003c/span\u003e(testimonial), and \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་ཡོད་\u003c/span\u003e (egophoric). These are formed by adding an existential copula to the suffix\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003e གི་\u003c/span\u003e. The resulting auxiliaries have the same evidential value as the existential copulas. In modern conversational usage, the form \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་འདུག་\u003c/span\u003e is often abbreviated to \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགིས་\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eIn English, these forms may be translated either by the progressive or the simple present depending on the context.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eThe various forms are presented in the following table:\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTable: The Present Tense Auxiliaries\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003ctable border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"\u003e \u003ctbody\u003e \u003ctr\u003e \u003ctd width=\"97\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eAffirmative\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"152\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eInterrogative\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e(without pronoun)\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"149\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eInterrogative\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e(with pronouns)\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"105\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eNegative\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"144\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eNegative Interrogative\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003c/tr\u003e \u003ctr\u003e \u003ctd width=\"97\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་ཡོད་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"152\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་ཡོད་པས་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"149\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་ཡོད་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"105\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་མེད་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"144\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་མེད་པས་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003c/tr\u003e \u003ctr\u003e \u003ctd width=\"97\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་འདུག་\u003c/span\u003e / \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགིས་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"152\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་འདུག་གས་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"149\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་འདུག་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"105\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་མི་འདུག་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"144\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་མི་འདུག་གས་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003c/tr\u003e \u003ctr\u003e \u003ctd width=\"97\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་ཡོད་རེད་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"152\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་ཡོད་རེད་པས་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"149\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་ཡོད་རེད་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"105\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་ཡོད་མ་རེད་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003ctd width=\"144\"\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགི་ཡོད་མ་རེད་པས་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/td\u003e \u003c/tr\u003e \u003c/tbody\u003e \u003c/table\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eSome basic example sentences:\u003c/p\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eང་ཁ་ལག་བཟོ་གི་ཡོད།\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;I am preparing the meal.\u0026rdquo; (or) \u0026ldquo;I prepare the meal.\u0026rdquo; (egophoric)\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eང་ཡི་གེ་འབྲི་གི་ཡོད།\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;I am writing a letter.\u0026rdquo; (or) \u0026ldquo;I write letters.\u0026rdquo; (egophoric)\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eབློ་བཟང་ཁ་ལག་བཟོ་གི་ཡོད་རེད།\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Lopzang prepares food.\u0026rdquo; (or) \u0026ldquo;Lopzang is preparing food.\u0026rdquo; (assertive)\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eབློ་བཟང་ཁ་ལག་བཟོ་གི་\u003c/span\u003e(\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eའདུག\u003c/span\u003e) \u0026ldquo;Lopzang is preparing food.\u0026rdquo; (or) \u0026ldquo;Lopzang prepares food.\u0026rdquo; (testimonial)\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརྡོ་རྗེ་ཡི་གེ་འབྲི་གི་ཡོད་རེད། \u003c/span\u003e\u0026ldquo;Dorj\u0026eacute; writes letters.\u0026rdquo; (or) \u0026ldquo;Dorj\u0026eacute; is writing a letter.\u0026rdquo; (assertive)\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརྡོ་རྗེ་ཡི་གེ་འབྲི་གི་\u003c/span\u003e(\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eའདུག\u003c/span\u003e) \u0026ldquo;Dorj\u0026eacute; is writing a letter.\u0026rdquo; (or) \u0026ldquo;Dorj\u0026eacute; writes letters.\u0026rdquo; (testimonial)\u003c/li\u003e \u003c/ul\u003e","source_url":null,"is_primary":true,"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:14:24 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:14:24 UTC","authors":[{"id":"6","fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre"}]}]}